M|Core|tx|**sl Proof Bar**
M|Core|it|cs logos (recognizable > many)
M|Core|it|Key metric ("10,000+ teams")
M|Core|it|Star rating w/ rv count
M|Core|it|Short testimonial snippet
M|Core|tx|**Problem/Pain Section**
M|Core|it|Articulate their problem better than they can
M|Core|it|cr recognition ("that's exactly my situation")
M|Core|it|Hint at cost of not solving it
M|Core|tx|**Solution/Benefits Section**
M|Core|it|Bridge from problem to your solution
M|Core|it|3-5 key benefits (not 10)
M|Core|- Ea|hl + explanation + proof if available
M|Core|tx|**How It Works**
M|Core|it|3-4 numbered steps
M|Core|it|Reduces perceived complexity
M|Core|- Ea|action + outcome
M|Core|tx|**Final CTA Section**
M|Core|it|Recap value proposition
M|Core|it|Repeat primary CTA
M|Core|it|Risk reversal (guarantee, free trial)
