M|Supp|tx|**Testimonials**
M|Supp|it|Full quotes w/ names, roles, companies
M|Supp|it|Photos when possible
M|Supp|it|Specific results over vague praise
M|Supp|- Fo|quote cards, vd, tweet embeds
M|Supp|tx|**Case Studies**
M|Supp|it|Problem → Solution → Results
M|Supp|it|Specific metrics and outcomes
M|Supp|it|cs name and context
M|Supp|it|Can be snippets w/ "Read more" links
M|Supp|tx|**Use Cases**
M|Supp|it|Different ways pd is used
M|Supp|it|Helps visitors self-identify
M|Supp|it|"For marketers who need X" format
M|Supp|tx|**Personas / "Built For" Sections**
M|Supp|it|Explicitly call out target audience
M|Supp|it|"Perfect for [role]" blocks
M|Supp|it|Addresses "Is this for me?" question
M|Supp|tx|**FAQ Section**
M|Supp|it|Address common objections
M|Supp|it|Good for SEO
M|Supp|it|Reduces support burden
M|Supp|it|5-10 most common questions
M|Supp|tx|**Comparison Section**
M|Supp|it|vs. cr (name them or don't)
M|Supp|it|vs. status quo (spreadsheets, manual processes)
M|Supp|it|Tables or side-by-side format
M|Supp|tx|**Integrations / Partners**
M|Supp|it|Logos of tools you connect w/
M|Supp|it|"Works w/ your stack" messaging
M|Supp|it|Builds credibility
M|Supp|tx|**Founder Story / Manifesto**
M|Supp|it|Why you built this
M|Supp|it|What you believe
M|Supp|it|Emotional connection
M|Supp|it|Differentiates from faceless cr
M|Supp|tx|**Demo / pd Tour**
M|Supp|it|Interactive demos
M|Supp|it|vd walkthroughs
M|Supp|it|GIF previews
M|Supp|it|Shows pd in action
